      "questionText": "<p>Match items of column I and II</p>\n<p><style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;width: 100%}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-1wig{font-weight:bold;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-baqh{text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-amwm{font-weight:bold;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-0lax{text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n</p><table class=\"tg\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;\">\n<colgroup>\n<col style=\"width: 59px\">\n<col style=\"width: 248px\">\n<col style=\"width: 58px\">\n<col style=\"width: 256px\">\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-amwm\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-1wig\">Column I (Mixture of compounds)</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-amwm\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-1wig\">Column II (Separation Technique)</th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">A.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">$$\\mathrm{H_2O/CH_2Cl_2}$$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">i.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Crystalization</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">B.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\"><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ldq0keti/38ad4a65-5544-4c27-a116-467740af6b0f/06662a60-a493-11ed-8eb4-ef270ed2fedb/file-1ldq0ketj.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ldq0keti/38ad4a65-5544-4c27-a116-467740af6b0f/06662a60-a493-11ed-8eb4-ef270ed2fedb/file-1ldq0ketj.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 31st January Morning Shift Chemistry - Basics of Organic Chemistry Question 139 English\"></td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">ii.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Differential solvent extraction</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">C.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Kerosene / Naphthalene</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">iii.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Column chromatography</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">D.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">$$\\mathrm{C_6H_{12}O_6/NaCl}$$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">iv.</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Fractional Distillation</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><p></p>\n<p>Correct match is </p>",
